"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-01-Paris-first-women-s-dragon-boat-team-appears-at-2024-Summer-Olympics-1vI9CNYP184-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  Dragon boat racing has been featured as a demonstration sport at the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 302, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Paris' first women's team of this exciting water sport, mainly composed of breast cancer survivors, participated in the torch relay.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 307, \"end\": 312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999974222314705, \"rank\": 2.5777751763784038e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since it was established in 2016, the team has been practicing on a weekly basis for the past eight years.\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Team leader Carole designed a logo with intertwined dragons and phoenixes, reflecting their journey of overcoming pain and rising anew.\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 682, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The team said it is proud to represent Chinese culture in Paris, especially during this milestone year for France-China relations.\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"score\": 0.9999999999989768, \"rank\": 8.683506626989019e-13, \"text\": \"Chinese culture\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_culture\", \"dbpedia\": \"http: